		<td><b>Re: GB/C Dev Environment?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Or, use <a href="http://bgb.bircd.org/" class="postlink">BGB</a>. 99% of the times, it emulates things correctly. (Make sure you have the latest version if you already have a copy on your hard drive, however. There has been some substantial improvement in several areas over the last two years.)

		

		</td>
